      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:01:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔讲话前，服务业指数疲软，阻止债券抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bond-selloff-halted-by-weak-services-gauge-before-powell-speaks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于服务业活动指标弱于预期，增强了人们对美联储本月将降息的预期，美国国债抛售势头停止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/bond-selloff-halted-by-weak-services-gauge-before-powell-speaks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:00:46 GMT</pubDate>
